// CollisionDomain ka mtlb hai ki jaise koi Bus-topology-LAN hai and usmeh obviously kuch n-devices connected honge, toh agr kisi ek time pe sabhi devices usi time pe signal(ya message) bhejteh hai, then mtlb voh sabhi message(signal) collide hojayenge and koi communication nhi hopayega. and toh esko apn aseh boltehh hai ki LAN meh Collision-Domain "n" hota hai.
// BroadCast-Domain mtlb  ki jaise koi LAN hai and usmeh agr koi ek device message send krta hai then voh message(ya signal) pure LAN meh broadcast hota hai, mtlb sabhi devices k pass jata hai, toh esko boltehh hai apn BroadCast-Domain ki message-signal kitne logo meh jayega, toh esko apn aseh boltehh hai ki LAN meh BroadCast-Domain "n" hota hai.

